sep.gaia.resources

Interface WorkerFactory<Q extends Query,R extends DataResource>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    LocationWorkerFactory, POIWorkerFactory, TileWorkerFactory, WikipediaWorkerFactory

    public interface WorkerFactory<Q extends Query,R extends DataResource>
    Class for generating new workers. This functionality is used by AbstractLoader when a query was split and will be processed. Implement this interface when defining own loaders and corresponding workers.
    Author:
    Matthias Fisch
